# Claude Code skill-creator evaluation artifacts
# skill-creator (https://github.com/anthropics/skills/tree/main/skills/skill-creator)
# runs A/B evals (with_skill vs without_skill) and writes results into
# *-workspace/ directories. These are machine-local throwaway outputs
# that should not be committed.
